Laurent,
you may have triggered the L2 eviction bug (E298).
Please try
hexdump -s 0xc0010015 -n 8 -C /dev/cpu/0/msr
Output is little-endian, so the left-most byte must have bit 3 enabled meaning 
TLB caching is disabled.
-Peter
